## Outputs

Write to `nav/{venue-slug}/`:

| File | Contents |
|------|----------|
| `ARCHITECTURE.md` | One-page system overview: sensor stack, fusion, map model, routing, UX |
| `SENSOR-FUSION.md` | Sensor choice rationale, fusion algorithm, motion + measurement models, convergence budget |
| `MAP-MODEL.md` | Graph schema, accessibility attributes, ingestion path, fingerprint layer |
| `ROUTING-RULES.md` | Per-persona constraints with concrete thresholds, citations (ADA / ICC A117.1 / ISO 21542) |
| `UX-FLOW.md` | Per-persona turn-by-turn UX, rerouting, failure-mode UX |
| `EVAL.md` | Ground-truth plan, metrics, drift bounds, on-device privacy posture |

Also append to `.gstack/decisions/indoor-nav-{venue-slug}.md` the citation
to Hall's PhD thesis and any thesis-derived assumptions used.

